    "title": "Pidilite Industries is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "We at Pidilite Industries are looking for an experienced Quality Control Engineer based out of Meerut. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Pidilite Industries:\nPidilite Industries is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Learning & development budget\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Pidilite Industries!",
